<h3 style="margin-bottom:-5px; margin-top:-10px;">What You Need to Know About BOB</h3>

<p>At CES 2017, we beta tested an innovative new beacon on badge technology exclusively for the C Space audience at ARIA. This program was aimed at enhancing our attendee&#39;s CES experience.<br />
<br />
BOBs were enabled with two-way communication technology that will enhance your on-site networking opportunities. BOB followed along your journey through the public spaces and lounges at ARIA, marking your digital path.</p>

<p>When attendees returned theirr BOB, we provided you with a link to your personalized journey timeline.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

